---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact Us - ToolCalcs"
  description="Get in touch with the ToolCalcs team. Report bugs, suggest new calculators, or ask questions."
>
  <div class="page-content">
    <h1>Contact Us</h1>
    <p>Have feedback, found a bug, or want to suggest a new calculator? We would love to hear from you.</p>

    <div class="contact-box">
      <h2>Get In Touch</h2>
      <p>Email us at: <a href="mailto:contact@toolcalcs.com">contact@toolcalcs.com</a></p>
    </div>

    <h2>What Can We Help With?</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Bug Reports:</strong> If a calculator is giving incorrect results, let us know which calculator and what inputs you used.</li>
      <li><strong>Calculator Suggestions:</strong> Want to see a new calculator? Tell us what you need.</li>
      <li><strong>General Feedback:</strong> We appreciate any suggestions to improve the site.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>We aim to respond within 2 business days.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-content { max-width: 700px; line-height: 1.8; }
  h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin: 28px 0 12px; }
  p { margin-bottom: 12px; }
  ul { margin: 0 0 16px 24px; }
  li { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .contact-box {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 24px;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }
  .contact-box h2 { margin-top: 0; }
</style>
